*Personalizing Patterns for Footwear Soles  "U.S. Patent 6,497,056".
*Cable Connector Crimping Apparatus  "U.S. Patent 4,143,459".
Three Dimensional Programmable Slide Rule  "U. S. Scientific Copyright" (1969). 
